name: 800 to 3000

video loop with sound. footage found on used VHS tape purchased at a local thrift shop. digitized with Elgato Game Capture HD60 S into OBS studio. post-production performed primarily in TouchDesigner with final tweaks and rendering in DaVinci Resolve. audio was thoroughly mangled by my Magnavox VCR's terrible tracking, granularized with a Make Noise Morphagene and Mutable Instruments Clouds (Typhoon) and distorted with a Plankton Electronics NuTone and Whimsical Raps Rip (Meng Qi ver.). final audio editing and production performed in Ableton Live 11 Suite.
